1003
01:28:18,500 --> 01:28:23,000
<i>Și voi fi mereu aproape</i>

1004
01:28:23,833 --> 01:28:27,750
<i>Aproape</i>

1005
01:28:47,166 --> 01:28:48,875
Ne uitam. Ne-ai văzut?

1006
01:28:49,375 --> 01:28:50,416
